Title: WARRIOR KINGS
Genre: Strategy - Real-time - Fantasy
Works on: Windows (XP, Vista, 7, 8, 10)
Languages: Audio and text: English
Features: single-player - multi-player
Released: April 13, 2002
Size: 486.9 MB
Company: Black Cactus Games / Strategy First
Rating:	ESRB Rating: Teen (with Blood, Violence)
Store page: http://www.gog.com/game/warrior_kings

About:
You are tasked with restoring the power of a kingdom to its former glory using innate cunning, military might and a fearsome will to win. Warrior Kings is an epic real-time strategy game that smashes the mold. Using true 3D, it propels you into a living, breathing, and fascinating medieval fantasy world.
Now it's all in your hands!
Build up your economic and military power base, research new technologies, and employ spies, mercenaries, priests and merchants to enhance your strength.
Use real military formations and tactics to conquer on the battlefield.
Master the skills of siege warfare and watch your troops sack mighty cities.
Conduct a massive campaign through 22 extraordinary levels made up of over 80 unique quests.

Minimum system requirements - Windows: XP / Vista / 7 / 8 / 10
Processor: 1.8 GHz or higher
Memory: 512 MB RAM (1 GB recommended)
Hard drive space: 800 MB
Sound: DirectX 9.0c-compatible sound card
Graphics: 256 MB VRAM or higher (ATI X600/GeForce 6800+ or better)
Keyboard, mouse
Compatibility notice: Intel graphics cards are not supported
